Invocation Name: press up coach
des:
Want to be able to do 100 press-ups? set yourself the challenge today! the press-coach will keep track of many you can do and give you information on trends and streaks as well as a little encouragement. 

Set the goal to whatever you want and let press-up coach help you achieve your targets today!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
